{"tid":147755,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 四人連線賽車 KART BATTLE #5 人人都有毛","createTime":"2017-03-08T05:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T05:44:18.000Z","uid":87951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca7cffc9baebecfd7ff2580da859f7406f22b8a","tid":147755,"uid":87951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/jp/r30/Purple71/v4/2f/e1/74/2fe174ab-7606-1860-f6be-27627dbd8abd/screen520x924.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa5.mzstatic.com%2Fjp%2Fr30%2FPurple71%2Fv4%2F2f%2Fe1%2F74%2F2fe174ab-7606-1860-f6be-27627dbd8abd%2Fscreen520x924.jpeg&h=a840d1c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://a2.mzstatic.com/jp/r30/Purple71/v4/9c/4d/5a/9c4d5a9f-220e-ab04-f8b6-afc7d10c3e30/screen520x924.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa2.mzstatic.com%2Fjp%2Fr30%2FPurple71%2Fv4%2F9c%2F4d%2F5a%2F9c4d5a9f-220e-ab04-f8b6-afc7d10c3e30%2Fscreen520x924.jpeg&h=f7140fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://a5.mzstatic.com/jp/r30/Purple71/v4/46/84/99/468499a5-adab-beb5-cd8d-f011ee8a5ded/screen520x924.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa5.mzstatic.com%2Fjp%2Fr30%2FPurple71%2Fv4%2F46%2F84%2F99%2F468499a5-adab-beb5-cd8d-f011ee8a5ded%2Fscreen520x924.jpeg&h=a4487c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暫時有以上卡通人物+ 2隻E神比你買,另外仲有一隻毛毛係乖既小朋友先有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩法好簡單,基本上同MARIO賽車一樣,支援4人連線,亦可以同FD一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://kartbattle.netmarble.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkartbattle.netmarble.jp%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=99a9fe82\" target=\"_blank\">http://kartbattle.netmarble.jp/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YFRqAIJvn3Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYFRqAIJvn3Y&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=ace5bfa3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YFRqAIJvn3Y</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲介紹: <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AUuQX_m6hPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAUuQX_m6hPU&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=cf577d7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AUuQX_m6hPU</a><br />\n<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/katobatoru-kart-battle/id1090649822?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fkatobatoru-kart-battle%2Fid1090649822%3Fmt%3D8&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=3c5bda08\" target=\"_blank\">http://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/katobatoru-kart-battle/id1090649822?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\nAN: <a href=\"http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.netmarble.boongjp&amp;hl=ja\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.netmarble.boongjp%26hl%3Dja&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=a3799316\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.netmarble.boongjp&amp;hl=ja</a><br />\n<br />\n1) 玩法大約係咁:<br />\n右下角禁比賽,再禁多下就RANDOM線上同人鬥,如果想同FD LIST既人鬥就禁右上&quot;紅綠燈&quot;再揀好友。<br />\nRANDOM戰有禮物同XP，同FD玩就有開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁有咩獎勵?<br />\n左下角有四格比你揀擺禮物，唔同禮物要唔同既時間先開到，有D 10幾秒,有D 12個鐘,每次只可以擺4份,擺滿左可以繼續比賽,但只係得XP,唔會有禮物收。<br />\n另外有2格佢會定時送野比你,禮物4個鐘有一份,最多一次過收2份,<br />\n拎夠10個獎杯又可以抽野(第1有3個,第2 2個,第3 1個), 拎完野又要等一排先可以拎過<br />\n<br />\n升LV有咩用?<br />\n電腦會RANDOM同你差唔多R.P.既人同你鬥,上到1700RP以上既紫章就係課長大戰(好似係)<br />\n而每一個月都會跟據你既分數有石同錢派,加上佢係計分唔係計人數，所以只要努力小小就好易上到最高RANK個LEAGUE<br />\n<br />\n另外亦都有得睇自己係全SER既排名，入去比賽個頁,右上角有個細個既頒獎台，禁入去就睇到=<br />\n<br />\nBY 22號寶寶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開POST template: <br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1hHuWxi-YAAzLrgocNU6_velFRlElQ98daiaJbwfz2sg/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1hHuWxi-YAAzLrgocNU6_velFRlElQ98daiaJbwfz2sg%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=ed526b16\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1hHuWxi-YAAzLrgocNU6_velFRlElQ98daiaJbwfz2sg/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;------------------------------------------------分隔線------------------------------------------&gt;<br />\n<br />\n3) 照睇所有車都可以升6星，佢有升星制度，但數值一定有差別。（未見素材，純估計） <br />\n依家7XX杯，有5條賽道玩，但仲未見到二星升三星&amp;#22021;素材，開箱又無、買又買唔到，可能要過1000杯先會有。 <br />\n暫時送&amp;#22021;米奇車幾好用，SR升到二星爆，應付7xx杯無乜大問題，配埋米奇加速技，好多跑道都應付到，由頭帶到尾。 <br />\n拎既石，可以抽一次車，抽一次素材，無位放箱都照打，高杯可能高獎勵<br />\nBY 蔣薇<br />\n<br />\n4)      IOS 點刷首抽?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前巴打可能講得唔太清楚新人睇唔明<br />\nIOS刷首抽唔洗DEL GAME<br />\n第一次未注冊又刷唔岩就去右上角齒輪＞SNS＞禁右下角disconnected<br />\n之後就注冊，呢個時候因為你未注冊過，所以佢係自動綁定你第一個AC<br />\n再去番右上角個齒輪到重覆番個步驟開完新AC佢就會問你D日文 你簡是就得<br />\nPS EMAIL唔一定要真實存在 求其打D英文數字@gmail.com都得<br />\nBY 全國最大的QQ<br />\n<br />\n5) 揀咩人揸車好?<br />\n每5lv要用金幣unlock 先可以繼續升,11lv有被動"},{"pid":"0ff32707b08fd5cf26a5d84663f901593001e6d1","tid":147755,"uid":87951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"胡迪<br />\n主動:向目標高速移動 被動:火箭變繩圈,加長技能時間<br />\n巴斯<br />\n主動:booster加速 被動: 加長booster 時間(每lv加5%),另外每10lv個booster 升1級,max lv 應該係紅色booster<br />\n米奇<br />\n主動: booster加速 被動:減食風CD<br />\n米妮<br />\n主動: booster加速 被動:提升start booster 既速度<br />\n唐老鴨<br />\n主動:無 被動:加錢<br />\nElsa<br />\n主動:放冰球 被動:一定機率擋冰球<br />\nAnna<br />\n主動: 放冰球 被動: 一定機率擋冰球<br />\nOlaf(雪人)<br />\n主動: 放冰球 被動: 一定機率擋冰球<br />\n小熊維尼<br />\n主動:放龜 被動:增強中龜效果時間<br />\n<br />\nBY 鬼月<br />\n<br />\n白E神<br />\n主動:盾  被動:升滿有69%擋道具<br />\n紅E神<br />\n主動:飛彈 被動:射飛彃後對手暈多3秒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lt;------------------------------------------------分隔線------------------------------------------&gt;<br />\nShare幾個網俾大家睇下，有講d基